Class AbstractHttpFeeder

  com.rexsl.log.AbstractHttpFeeder

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class AbstractHttpFeeder
extends Object
implements Feeder

Abstract feeder through HTTP POST request.

The class has to be public in order to allow LOG4J to access it.

The class is thread-safe.
